{
  "texts": [
    "To get a deeper understanding of the capability of AUTOACT, we manually compare the quality of trajectories generated by different methods from five aspects.",
    "We ask five NLP volunteers to individually select the optimal trajectories generated by all methods in terms of the number of planning rounds, the logical correctness of thoughts, action types, action parameters, and overall coherence.",
    "The final results are determined based on major votes.",
    "During the evaluation, it is hidden for the evaluators of the correspondence between the trajectories and the methods.",
    "We delete the reflection-related parts from the trajectories generated by AUTOACT and randomly shuffle the order of trajectories of each method in each data to minimize the potential bias as much as possible."
  ]
}